{"pageContext":{"posts":[{"excerpt":"mongodb常用命令 1、创建数据库 简便方法：写配置文件，例如在d盘下面的db文件件下建立三个文件夹\ndata、log、conf,然后在conf文件夹中建立一个mongod.conf的配置\n配置文件， 然后在d盘根目录下运行 2、连接mongodb 3、显示数据库中所有的数据库列表 4、使用某个数据库 5、插入数据 6、删除数据 7、更新数据 8、查询 更多参考： http://www.runoob.com/mongodb/mongodb-tutorial.html","html":"<h2 id=\"mongodb常用命令\"><a href=\"#mongodb%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>mongodb常用命令</h2>\n<h4 id=\"1、创建数据库\"><a href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1、创建数据库</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ mongodb --dbpath your-dbpath --port your-port   \n--logpath your-logpath\negg:\n$ mongodb --dbpath d:\\db\\data --port 27017   \n--logpath d:\\db\\log</code></pre></div>\n<p>简便方法：写配置文件，例如在d盘下面的db文件件下建立三个文件夹\ndata、log、conf,然后在conf文件夹中建立一个mongod.conf的配置\n配置文件，</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">dbpath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d:\\\\db\\\\data\nlogpath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d:\\\\db\\\\log\\\\mongod.log\nport <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 27017</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后在d盘根目录下运行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ mongod --port 27017 -f db/conf/mongod.conf</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"2、连接mongodb\"><a href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5mongodb\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2、连接mongodb</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ mongo --port your-port\negg:\n$ mongo --port 27017</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"3、显示数据库中所有的数据库列表\"><a href=\"#3%E3%80%81%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3、显示数据库中所有的数据库列表</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ show dbs</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"4、使用某个数据库\"><a href=\"#4%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%9F%90%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4、使用某个数据库</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ use db_name\negg:\n$ use <span class=\"token function\">test</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"5、插入数据\"><a href=\"#5%E3%80%81%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5、插入数据</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ db.test.insert<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>key1:value1,key2:value2,<span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\negg:\n$ db.test.insert<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"zhangsan\"</span>,<span class=\"token string\">\"age\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"14\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"6、删除数据\"><a href=\"#6%E3%80%81%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6、删除数据</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ db.test.remove<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>key:value<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\negg:\n$ db.test.remove<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"zhangsan\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"7、更新数据\"><a href=\"#7%E3%80%81%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7、更新数据</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ db.test.update<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>query<span class=\"token operator\">></span>,\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>update<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    upsert: <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>boolean<span class=\"token operator\">></span>,\n    multi: <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>boolean<span class=\"token operator\">></span>,\n    writeConcern: <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>document<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\negg:\n$ db.test.update<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"zhangsan\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>,<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token variable\">$set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lisi\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"8、查询\"><a href=\"#8%E3%80%81%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>8、查询</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ db.test.find<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>query<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\negg:\n$ db.test.find<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> //查询所有数据\n$ db.test.find<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lisi\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>更多参考：<a href=\"http://www.runoob.com/mongodb/mongodb-tutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://www.runoob.com/mongodb/mongodb-tutorial.html</a></p>","id":"f836df29-a40f-50e7-be7f-7f414e1624d6","fields":{"slug":"mongodb常用命令"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2016-06-11","title":"mongodb常用命令","category":"Tech","tags":["mongodb","database"],"banner":""},"timeToRead":2}],"tagName":"mongodb"}}